<subSubSection id="24CB1080FFB9FFE7FAB2AA8A8188F882" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="6C6E430BFFB9FFE7FAB2AA8A8188F882" blockId="13.[151,1437,1148,1895]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFB9FFE7FAB2AA8A815EFA1A" bold="true" box="[199,315,1508,1534]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Remarks.</emphasis>
Previous records from the coast of São Paulo include Ubatuba, Santos-São Vicente, and Cananéia (
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB9FFE7FAEAA96681E1F9C6" author="Gusmao, J. &amp; Lazoski, C. &amp; Monteiro, F. A. &amp; Sole-Cava, A. M." box="[159,388,1544,1571]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="491 - 502" refId="ref63939" refString="Gusmao, J., Lazoski, C., Monteiro, F. A. &amp; Sole-Cava, A. M. (2006) Cryptic species and population structuring of the Atlantic and Pacific seabob shrimp species, Xiphopenaeus kroyeri and Xiphopenaeus riveti. Marine Biology, 149 (3), 491 - 502. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / s 00227 - 005 - 0232 - x" type="journal article" year="2006">
Gusmão 
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFB9FFE7FB73A967815CF9C6" box="[262,313,1544,1570]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">et al</emphasis>
. 2006
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB9FFE7FBE5A96682EFF9C6" author="Piergiorge, R. M. &amp; Pontes, M. N. &amp; Duarte, A. V. B. &amp; Gusmao, J." box="[400,650,1544,1571]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="348 - 353" refId="ref73436" refString="Piergiorge, R. M., Pontes, M. N., Duarte, A. V. B. &amp; Gusmao, J. (2014) Haplotype-specific single-locus multiplex PCR assay for molecular identification of sea-bob shrimp, Xiphopenaeus kroyeri (Heller, 1862), cryptic species from the Southwest Atlantic using a DNA pooling strategy for simultaneous identification of multiple samples. Biochemical Systematics and Ecology, 54, 348 - 353. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / j. bse. 2014.03.023" type="journal article" year="2014">
Piergiorge 
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFB9FFE7F879A967825AF9C6" box="[524,575,1544,1570]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">et al</emphasis>
. 2014
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB9FFE7F8E3A96683BEF9C6" author="Carvalho-Batista, A. &amp; Terossi, M. &amp; Zara, F. J. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Costa, R. C." box="[662,987,1544,1571]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="15281" refId="ref56822" refString="Carvalho-Batista, A., Terossi, M., Zara, F. J., Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Costa, R. C. (2019) A multigene and morphological analysis expands the diversity of the seabod shrimp Xiphopenaeus Smith, 1869 (Decapoda: Penaeidae), with descriptions of two new species. Scientific Reports, 9, 15281. https: // doi. org / 10.1038 / s 41598 - 019 - 51484 - 3" type="journal article" year="2019">
Carvalho-Batista 
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFB9FFE7F929A96783EBF9C6" box="[860,910,1544,1570]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">et al</emphasis>
. 2019
</bibRefCitation>
). The geographical range of the species can be wider and the all-previous records (before 2019) of some populations must be cautiously considered because these studies did not differentiate 
<taxonomicName id="ABD13888FFB9FFE7F815A93E833DF98E" baseAuthorityName="Heller" baseAuthorityYear="1862" box="[608,856,1616,1642]" class="Malacostraca" family="Penaeidae" genus="Xiphopenaeus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kroyeri">
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFB9FFE7F815A93E833DF98E" box="[608,856,1616,1642]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Xiphopenaeus kroyeri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from the other two congeneric Atlantic species, 
<taxonomicName id="ABD13888FFB9FFE7FFF1A93F83E3F96A" authority="Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto &amp; Costa, 2020" authorityName="Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto &amp; Costa" authorityYear="2020" class="Malacostraca" family="Penaeidae" genus="Xiphopenaeus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dincao">
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFB9FFE7FFF1A93F8086F96A" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">X. dincao</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB9FFE7FA99A91A83E3F96A" author="Carvalho-Batista, A. &amp; Terossi, M. &amp; Zara, F. J. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Costa, R. C." box="[236,902,1652,1679]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="597 - 599" refId="ref56908" refString="Carvalho-Batista, A., Terossi, M., Zara, F. J., Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Costa, R. C. (2020) Validation of Xiphopenaeus dincao Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto and Costa and Xiphopenaeus baueri Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto and Costa (Decapoda: Penaeidae) from western Atlantic. Zootaxa, 4772 (3), 597 - 599. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4772.3.10" type="journal article" year="2020">Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto &amp; Costa, 2020</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="ABD13888FFB9FFE7F9B4A91B81D8F956" authority="Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto &amp; Costa, 2020" authorityName="Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto &amp; Costa" authorityYear="2020" class="Malacostraca" family="Penaeidae" genus="Xiphopenaeus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="baueri">
<emphasis id="5EA59F19FFB9FFE7F9B4A91B844EF96A" box="[961,1067,1652,1678]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">X. baueri</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB9FFE7FE41A91A81D8F956" author="Carvalho-Batista, A. &amp; Terossi, M. &amp; Zara, F. J. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Costa, R. C." pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="597 - 599" refId="ref56908" refString="Carvalho-Batista, A., Terossi, M., Zara, F. J., Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Costa, R. C. (2020) Validation of Xiphopenaeus dincao Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto and Costa and Xiphopenaeus baueri Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto and Costa (Decapoda: Penaeidae) from western Atlantic. Zootaxa, 4772 (3), 597 - 599. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4772.3.10" type="journal article" year="2020">Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto &amp; Costa, 2020</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
