<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB9FFE7FEE3A9F685F4F956" author="Khafage, A. R. &amp; Taha, S. M." box="[1174,1425,1688,1714]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="392 - 399" refId="ref66075" refString="Khafage, A. R. &amp; Taha, S. M. (2019) First record of Xiphopenaeus kroyeri Heller, 1862 (Decapoda, Penaeidae) in the Southeastern Mediterranean, Egypt. BioInvasions Record, 8 (2), 392 - 399. https: // doi. org / 10.3391 / bir. 2019.8.2.20" type="journal article" year="2019">Khafage &amp; Taha 2019</bibRefCitation>
