<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB9FFE7FEA8A86A8171F8A6" author="Carvalho-Batista, A. &amp; Terossi, M. &amp; Zara, F. J. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Costa, R. C." pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="15281" refId="ref56822" refString="Carvalho-Batista, A., Terossi, M., Zara, F. J., Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Costa, R. C. (2019) A multigene and morphological analysis expands the diversity of the seabod shrimp Xiphopenaeus Smith, 1869 (Decapoda: Penaeidae), with descriptions of two new species. Scientific Reports, 9, 15281. https: // doi. org / 10.1038 / s 41598 - 019 - 51484 - 3" type="journal article" year="2019">
