</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="08403EFAFFB9FFE7FB54A846813BF8A6" author="Carvalho-Batista, A. &amp; Terossi, M. &amp; Zara, F. J. &amp; Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Costa, R. C." box="[289,350,1832,1858]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="597 - 599" refId="ref56908" refString="Carvalho-Batista, A., Terossi, M., Zara, F. J., Mantelatto, F. L. &amp; Costa, R. C. (2020) Validation of Xiphopenaeus dincao Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto and Costa and Xiphopenaeus baueri Carvalho-Batista, Terossi, Zara, Mantelatto and Costa (Decapoda: Penaeidae) from western Atlantic. Zootaxa, 4772 (3), 597 - 599. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4772.3.10" type="journal article" year="2020">2020</bibRefCitation>
